sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant App as Your App
    participant Auth as Auth Provider
    participant API as Your API

    User->>App: 1. Click "Login"
    App->>Auth: 2. Redirect to /authorize
    Auth->>User: 3. Login & Consent screen
    User->>Auth: 4. Grant access
    Auth->>App: 5. Redirect with auth code
    App->>Auth: 6. POST /token (code + client_secret)
    Auth->>App: 7. Access token + Refresh token
    App->>API: 8. API request with Bearer token
    API->>App: 9. Protected resource
